            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29147164">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">放眼他的四周，灯光霓虹交错如一条银河，脉搏跳动，吞没了一个叫老十的女孩。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-10-29 21:01</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
